All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UIMA_UnsupportedOperationException
extends UIMARuntimeException

Thrown to indicate that the requested operation is not supported. This extends RuntimeException and so does not need to be delcared in the throws clause of methods.

See Also:
